OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,FThe court stated that the Co-op
OL,7,F"failed in its duty of care", causing
OL,8,FMr MacLeod "psychiatric ill health"
OL,9,Fthrough a sustained and unjustified
OL,10,Fcampaign to force him from office.
OL,12,FThe judgment ruled that three non-
OL,13,Fexecutive directors of the Society's
OL,14,FRemuneration Committee (RemCo) had
OL,15,Facted in bad faith from early 2019
OL,16,Funtil Mr Macleod's dismissal in mid-
OL,17,F2020, after his 30-year career working
OL,18,Ffor the society.
