OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,FThe Channel Islands Co-op has
OL,7,Facknowledged the judgment, but says it
OL,8,F"does not agree" with the findings and
OL,9,Fthat they will appeal the decision.
OL,11,FMr Macleod was awarded a further
OL,12,F#40,000 in general damages for the
OL,13,Finjury, which led to him being signed
OL,14,Foff from work in May 2019, despite
OL,15,Fstill being the CEO.
OL,17,FThe organisation's insurance will
OL,18,Fcover the payout.
