OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Macleod said:
OL,7,F"I've got this melting pot of
OL,8,Femotions. On the one hand, very sad
OL,9,Fthat I've had to fight this fight. On
OL,10,Fthe other, I'm very proud to have
OL,11,Ffought.
OL,13,F"This was a sinister and horrible case
OL,14,Fof board dysfunction, infighting,
OL,15,Fpersonal ambition and abandonment of
OL,16,Fvalues that have held the Society in
OL,17,Fgood stead for over a hundred years.
OL,19,F"The money is just a consequence of
OL,20,Fthe actions that I took.
