OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,F"I fell in love with the co-operative
OL,7,Fidea when I was 20. That hasn't
OL,8,Fchanged. I'm not standing against the
OL,9,FCo-op or what it stands for, only
OL,10,Fagainst those that abandoned those
OL,11,Fprinciples and values in favour of
OL,12,Fpursuing their own personal agendas."
OL,14,FRemCo's chair, Jennifer Carnegie, was
OL,15,Fsaid to be the 'ringleader' seeking to
OL,16,Fremove Mr MacLeod, supported by two
OL,17,Fother non-executive Co-op board
OL,18,Fdirectors, Paula Williams and Carol
OL,19,FChampion.
