OL,6,FThe court ruled their campaign
OL,7,Fincluded secret WhatsApp and email
OL,8,Fmessages, "laser-focused" expense
OL,9,Faudits, and "robust appraisal" of his
OL,10,Fperformance.
OL,12,FOne message written by Ms Champion and
OL,13,Fshared with colleagues said: "(...)
OL,14,Fwhen the noose starts tightening, you
OL,15,Fget more stressed and end up off from
OL,16,Fwork", in relation to Mr Macleod.
