OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,FChannel Islands Co-op's president, Ben
OL,7,FShenton, is also said to have failed
OL,8,Fin his responsibilities by encouraging
OL,9,FMr Macleod to complain about his
OL,10,Ftreatment, leading Ms Carnegie to
OL,11,Foffer her resignation.
OL,13,FHowever, Mr Shenton then neither
OL,14,Faccepted Ms Carnegie's resignation nor
OL,15,Fasked Ms Williams to step down after
OL,16,Fshe had inappropriately applied for Mr
OL,17,FMacleod's role as CEO.
