OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,FChannel Islands Co-op has stated: "The
OL,7,FChannel Islands Co-op acknowledges the
OL,8,Fjudgment of the Royal Court, but, with
OL,9,Frespect, it does not agree with the
OL,10,Ffindings made by the Court.
OL,12,F"The Society has liaised closely with
OL,13,Fits insurers and legal advisers, and
OL,14,Fit is considered that there are
OL,15,Fsubstantial grounds for appeal and the
OL,16,Fjudgment will be challenged."
OL,18,FFollowing the ruling, Mr Macleod said:
OL,19,F"It is with a heavy heart that I
OL,20,Freflect on the court's findings.
