OL,3,CEx-Co-op boss awarded millions after
OL,4,C'appalling' smear campaign against him
OL,6,F"It is profoundly disappointing that,
OL,7,Fin the end, it took the Royal Court to
OL,8,Fenforce the values of The Channel
OL,9,FIslands Co-operative Society.
OL,11,F"The Board of Directors had countless
OL,12,Fopportunities to fix this mess quietly
OL,13,Fand with dignity, but on each of those
OL,14,Foccasions it chose not to.
OL,16,F"Members now must surely have a right
OL,17,Fto know why."
